Royal Bank of Scotland ups mortgage rate . The Royal Bank of Scotland said on Tuesday it has raised its mortgage rate to 7 . 25 percent from 6 . 99 percent for both new and existing customers with effect from January 1 . The bank said it was also reviewing its savings rates . Most other major lenders increased their rates by a similar amount last week . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7717 . 
